title: Start
body:
Frank: Hey, it's me. Frank.
Sammy: W-who?
Frank: Frank! Ya know?
Sammy: Umm. N-no, I don't... know?
[[Why don't you know?|WhyNot]]
[[Anyways, whatever.|Whatever]]

title: WhyNot
body:
Frank: Why not?
Sammy: Because this is stupid.

title: Whatever
body:
Frank: Whatever.
Sammy: That's the spirit!
